Name: PLR_DK_IHE_TypeCode
Title: PLR-DK IHE TypeCode
Descriptino: PLR-DK: Value set for the typeCode attribute. The typeCode specifies the precise type of document from the user perspective. The granularity of typeCode is finer grained than its superior classCode.

Name: MedComIHE_CoreHealthcareFacilityTypeCode
Title: IHE HealthcareFacilityTypeCode
Descriptino: Value set for healthcare facility type code represents the type of organizational setting of the clinical encounter during which the documented act occurred.

Name: MedComIHE_CorePracticeSettingCode
Title: IHE PracticeSettingCode
Descriptino: Values used for the document metadata attribute practiceSettingCode, which is an attribute specifying the clinical specialty where the act that resulted in the document was performed (e.g., Family Practice, Laboratory, Radiology). The value set is based on a subset of the code list from the SOR lookup table 'SOR-Kliniske specialer' (https://sor.sum.dsdn.dk/lookupdata/#clinical_speciality, accessable on Sundhedsdatanettet (SDN)), which is based on SNOMED codes.

Name: MedComIHE_CoreClassCode
Title: IHE ClassCode
Descriptino: Value set for the classCode attribute. classCode used in DK IHE Document sharing

Name: MedComIHE_ConfidentialityCode
Title: IHE ConfidentialityCode
Descriptino: Confidentiality code used in Danish Document sharing.

Name: MedComIHE_CoreDkHomeCommunityId
Title: IHE HomeCommunityId
Descriptino: List of operational and in production home communities (XCA) in Danish Document Sharing

Name: MedComIHE_CoreLanguageCode
Title: IHE LanguageCode
Descriptino: Tags for the Identification of Languages (RFC 3066)

Name: MedComIHE_CoreMimeType
Title: IHE MimeType
Descriptino: Values for the document metadata attribute mimeType

Name: MedComIHE_PLR_DK_FormatCode
Title: PLR-DK IHE FormatCode
Descriptino: PLR-DK: Code system for document format code used in national Document sharing. The value set for format code is based on code system DK_IHE_FormatCode.
